Source: ws-audiod
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ed Baker <ed@ebaker.me.uk>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cmake, libasound2-dev, libsndfile1-dev, pkg-config
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/Wildlife-Systems/ws-audiod

Package: ws-audiod
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Multi-consumer audio capture daemon
 ws-audiod provides continuous ALSA audio capture with concurrent
 multi-consumer access through a single device interface. Features
 include ring-buffer clip extraction, gapless block recording, and
 zero-copy shared memory distribution.
